=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5045d0733332aa8ad16d648ca2f6694629aebc5","tid":1981490,"uid":36162,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:51:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">落後一代</span></strong>的殲-15艦載機<br />\n根本打都唔打得, 點落後一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6048d631acd862c7e21bdbd2e6c1c6351e5d9c1a","tid":1981490,"uid":227271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:51:58.000Z","msg":"D細狗最鐘意對住d大狗吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef43046997554ea05ae3e470db69ca6585445de","tid":1981490,"uid":271894,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:52:06.000Z","msg":"包住人做咩姐<br />\n開雷達lock 佢 準備㩒制先好玩嫁嗎"},{"pid":"c3a5cf45affc73dca305c535da822db29c6fbba3","tid":1981490,"uid":23194,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:54:43.000Z","msg":"就係呢啲廢文令到藍屍廢佬以為中國好好打<br />\n係呀，北洋艦隊打之前都係咁"},{"pid":"e09faec2f6ca47c5406209081428c7ee41185f26","tid":1981490,"uid":293677,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eX4exmR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeX4exmR.jpg&h=6754d1a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a68a87ac2d1063dbeddfcfa79ac81693347c1a2a","tid":1981490,"uid":320074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:58:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">借個位先 召喚聯署師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzTizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=2cb11b05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">裡面有好多為香港打定安全網既聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如我地唔打好 我地好難用<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最低程度既損傷</span><br />\n去真正<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 奪權當家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n前一兩日李柱銘俾狗塔，但喺美國政壇引起如此大既迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。正係<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為先前聯署同請求美帝落實《人權及民主法案》而致</span>，趁機<span style=\"color: teal;\">俾藉口美帝加速打殘狗共</span>，何樂不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A部分請㩒入去呢度<br />\n記得睇埋啊，好撚緊要啊</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">【偽 &middot; 正視聽】得啦我知我洗咗你地版<br />\n召喚聯署師長文Q&amp;A就放喺度啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1981260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1981260</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"a153886baaa1504b3d29d69bb7aa481f97ac6c5f","tid":1981490,"uid":166729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:59:05.000Z","msg":"人地飛晒d F35上天, 你仲係度on99咋"},{"pid":"e406cc449ffbe8c8e4f2e6f3ecdd687d375373dd","tid":1981490,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5045d0733332aa8ad16d648ca2f6694629aebc5","tid":1981490,"uid":36162,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:51:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">落後一代</span></strong>的殲-15艦載機<br />\n根本打都唔打得, 點落後一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:59:23.000Z","msg":"落後一個時代<br />\n講緊機關槍打火繩槍<br />\n<br />\n快你5秒就係我屌到你你屌唔到我嘅分別"},{"pid":"cce8309a26bea1bc3b2ccb40cad61c49772cff81","tid":1981490,